<!--
VOICING PLAN: Key F (1 flat). Dm area melody (same tune as 4148 transposed to F).
LH: F F2-C3-F3-A3; Dm D2-A2-D3-F3; Bb Bb2-F3-Bb3-D4; Gm G2-D3-G3-Bb3.
Climax bars 7-9 with higher register RH (D5-E5-F5).
TEXTURE ARC: Simple F tonic open; Dm-Bb area darkens; return to F close.
-->
